text: Herry Janto Setiawan (10 August 1973 - 10 October 2013) was an Indonesian cyclist. He competed in the track time trial at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:2013 deaths Category:Indonesian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Indonesia Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
